con:testCase.name: RemoveFraudPayment
con:testCase.con:description:
This testcase displays the flow of the PIN Action: Remove Fraud flag in Paymemt. Here an inernational payment is created. The then actions Remove fraud flag performed on the payment.
Expected Flow: Payment Create (Future Value Date) -> with Fraud Status ->AFIP --> Remove Fraud flag
